tplinkIpv6AddrMIB.name: tplinkIpv6AddrMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tplinkIpv6AddrMIB.description: Private MIB for IPv6 address configuration.

ipv6ParaConfigAddrTable.name: ipv6ParaConfigAddrTable
ipv6ParaConfigAddrTable.description: The table of address information is relevant to the switch's IPv6 addresses.

ipv6ParaConfigAddrType.name: ipv6ParaConfigAddrType
ipv6ParaConfigAddrType.description: The IP address type of the switch. The value must be ipv6.

ipv6ParaConfigAddress.name: ipv6ParaConfigAddress
ipv6ParaConfigAddress.description: The IPv6 address of the switch.

ipv6ParaConfigPrefixLength.name: ipv6ParaConfigPrefixLength
ipv6ParaConfigPrefixLength.description: The length of the prefix (in bits) associated with the IPv6 address of the switch.

ipv6ParaConfigSourceType.name: ipv6ParaConfigSourceType
ipv6ParaConfigSourceType.description: Indicate the type of source of IPv6 address. The value can be one of following: 'assignedIp': Assigned global/site-local IPv6 address; 'assignedEUI64Ip': Assigned global/site-local IPv6 address by using EUI-64 interface identifier; 'assignedLinklocalIp': Assigned link-local IPv6 address. 'autoIp': Auto generated IPv6 address as a result of non-linklocal anycast/unicast address configuration; 'dhcpv6': Assigned IPv6 address through DHCPv6 protocol; 'negotiate': Assigned IPv6 address through negotiation;

ipv6ParaConfigRowStatus.name: ipv6ParaConfigRowStatus
ipv6ParaConfigRowStatus.description: the following values are states: these values may be used as follow: active(1),if the entry is being used. notInService(2),destory the entry. notReady(3),destory the entry. createAndGo(4),not being used createAndWait(5),creat a new entry destroy(6),destory the entry. When you create a new user,the default password is admin.
